metadata.name: Symbolic
metadata.description:
The first piece, is an open edition, to be dropped on our Moving Messages Contract.  This piece will be open for a undetermined amount of time (no more than 10,000 pieces). In the future these pieces will be set to burn for redeeming other more rare, artworks. 
 Symbolic is only the beginning of the Moving Messages artworks. 

There will also be a 1 eth giveaway after half of the pieces mint. Followed by a 2 Eth giveaway after all pieces are minted out!
